{"tid":2394899,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中英再起爭拗 英國封殺央視","createTime":"2021-02-04T13:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T00:58:41.000Z","uid":28114,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4619214e5d95f9a23c371193d775eee6c3f2cf9b","tid":2394899,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Hnb6P2S6KRc/YBvh-gABXTI/AAAAAAAAHuw/hwDMW1ZabZ4oDGuyi4Egu9cHFFwuLfBVQCLcBGAsYHQ/s497/cgtnHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Hnb6P2S6KRc%2FYBvh-gABXTI%2FAAAAAAAAHuw%2FhwDMW1ZabZ4oDGuyi4Egu9cHFFwuLfBVQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs497%2FcgtnHK.jpg&h=c5e7009a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/02/CGTN.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F02%2FCGTN.html%3Fm%3D1&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRFiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=2c093d29\" target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/02/CGTN.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n【本文上載於英國時間中午12時1分，更新於12時42分】<br />\n<br />\n繼香港、華為等問題後，英國跟中國又有新的爭拗。英國電訊管理局Ofcom今天（4日）宣佈，收回中央電視台面向國際的廣播「中國環球電視網」（CGTN）在英國的牌照，CGTN不能在英國播放。<br />\n<br />\n在英國，CGTN的播放牌照由一間叫做「星空華文傳媒」的企業擁有。<br />\nOfcom說，根據英國法例，廣播牌照持有者需要能對其播放內容作出控制，包括編輯監管，但Ofcom調查後，認為星空華文不能控制CGTN播放什麼，這間公司沒有任何員工參與CGTN內容的製作或監察，因此撤銷其廣播牌照。<br />\n<br />\nOfcom又說，不能把這個牌照直接轉讓給CGTN，因為CGTN最終是由中共直接控制，這違反了英國法例。聲明說，已給予CGTN足夠時間解釋及嘗試符合規例，但CGTN仍然做不到。<br />\n<br />\n公開道歉影片爭拗<br />\n<br />\nOfcom跟CGTN的爭拗，最早源於Peter Humphrey事件。<br />\n<br />\nHumphrey是英國公民，原本工作是調查員，但在中國替客戶調查一宗涉嫌貪污案期間，2013年被捕，然後央視在2013和2014年兩度播出他公開認罪及道歉的片段。<br />\n<br />\n影片也有透過CGTN在英國播放。Humphrey向Ofcom投訴，影片不公平對待他，令人誤以為他是自願認罪，又說影片侵犯了他的私隱，認為這些都違反了英國廣播守則。<br />\n<br />\nOfcom在去年7月裁定Humphrey的投訴成立，CGTN違反了英國廣播守則。<br />\n<br />\n香港反修例示威<br />\n<br />\n另外，Ofcom去年5月也裁定，CGTN對2019年香港反修例示威的報導，嚴重違反英國廣播守則。<br />\n<br />\nOfcom認為，CGTN有關香港示威的內容嚴重偏頗，只播放示威者對警察施暴，卻淡化當局對示威者的攻擊，亦沒有報導反北京的意見。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，CGTN在2018年才於倫敦建立了歐洲總部，以拓展對歐洲新聞的採訪，以及增加向歐洲廣播。現在不能在英國廣播，或多或少會對中國官媒在歐洲的發展有影響。<br />\n<br />\n不過，CGTN跟英國Ofcom已爭拗多時，去年秋天傳出，CGTN計劃在比利時布魯塞爾設立辦公室，相信是為一旦在英發展受阻而作準備。"},{"pid":"6f59035c0429cdb2bf5af040d2c8e55e99cfff25","tid":2394899,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"Ofcom revokes Chinese broadcaster CGTN's UK licence<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-55931548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-55931548&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRFiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=0878435b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-55931548&h=d4cba6ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-55931548</a>"},{"pid":"7235298afaca98e1e77c02593e0eb900e341a84d","tid":2394899,"uid":8308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"歐美醒醒定定趕晒d支資走啦"},{"pid":"95dfe84da3e40925b6d9582309322c8e14e5924e","tid":2394899,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又撚支那Joe"},{"pid":"9c5070ac0e690a8dade1cf5c2945526c26a43c9b","tid":2394899,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"恭喜晒"},{"pid":"1a01fbb0563f7888b28d757fb96906572ce5c12b","tid":2394899,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"打啦，好悶呀"},{"pid":"38f59b93e5803a19a4234f4fb844f2226390b46c","tid":2394899,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:28:23.000Z","msg":"Ban喇 <br />\n共產黨唔比人入支那市場 點解其他國家要比佢地做大外宣"},{"pid":"80834417c109650d0d333f83d2a884b88b042889","tid":2394899,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc